<br>
::He walked foward a bit:: &quot;Tartarus can be such a depressing place, and I just happened to be in the neighborhood.&quot;  ::His dark sarcasm at work yet again, he was on a role, for he rarely stayed sarcastic for long.::<br>
<br>
&quot;As for them...&quot; ::Motioning to the other &quot;dark&quot; gods in the room::  &quot;They can answer as to the reason for their presense on their own.&quot;<br>
