<br>
He looks to Hades as he appeared,and bows slightly in respect,then turned his attention to Apollo. A simple little smirk played on his pale lips,but nodded in respect for the golden god. <br>
<br>
He watches Megaera for a short moment,and smiled lightly,something rare for him to do,but that smile immediatly faded,and he was back to looking emotionless.<br>
<br>
