<br>
::At first he was not going to even acknowledge Mad Mardigan's presenece.  It did not concern him.  However his interest was tweaked once he whispered to Apollo and then Apollo pulled him aside::<br>
<br>
&quot;So what do you think Mardigan is informing Apollo about?  Which one of us does he fear that he must speak to Apollo beyond our range of hearing?  Perhaps all?  Perhaps none?&quot;<br>
<br>
::He smile coily deciding to rouse suspicion among the 'dark gods', to get them to think a little bit.::<br>
<br>
&quot;As for me personally, I shall take the stance I normally take, and just not care.  Worry about it when his lifeline is snuffed out and he becomes a subject in MY kingdom.&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#336699><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/udarkestnyx.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Darkest Nyx</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_magentaspot.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 22<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(2/21/02 8:27 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=233.topic&index=37>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.skintwo.com/clothing/pix/garments/standard/sk1072.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: A dark smile...</span><hr size=1> :~: She looked to Hades as he spoke his question about Mad and Apollo and shrugged.:~:<br>
